targets.rawSql: select  CONCAT(iface,'___', ip,'___', kbps,'___', classe) as "INFO", now() as time from rede where hostname = '$hostname' and ativo = 't' group by iface, ip, kbps, classe order by classe;

list.definition: select distinct substring(p.nome::text,1,2) from ponto p, cliente c where substring(p.id::text,1,4) = c.id::text and c.sigla = 'MODELO';
list.label: UF
list.name: uf
list.query: select distinct substring(p.nome::text,1,2) from ponto p, cliente c where substring(p.id::text,1,4) = c.id::text and c.sigla = 'MODELO';

list.definition: select p.nome from ponto p, cliente c where substring(p.id::text,1,4) = c.id::text and substring(p.nome::text,1,2) = '$uf' and c.sigla = 'MODELO' order by 1;
list.label: Localidade
list.name: localidade
list.query: select p.nome from ponto p, cliente c where substring(p.id::text,1,4) = c.id::text and substring(p.nome::text,1,2) = '$uf' and c.sigla = 'MODELO' order by 1;

list.definition: select hostname from ponto where nome = '$localidade'
